data.description: This charming home has been lovingly updated and is ready for its new owners! The natural color palette, fresh interior paint and new flooring throughout the home make it a warm and inviting space. The kitchen boasts stone counter tops, tile backsplash and new appliances. The primary bathroom features double sinks and custom tile shower. There are additional rooms for flexible living space. A cozy fireplace adds ambiance to the living area. Step outside to the sitting area in the backyard and relax. This home is move-in ready and just waiting for you to make it your own. Come take a look today! This home has been virtually staged to illustrate its potential.
